  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791460/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1639777991\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791460/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1639777991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791460/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1639777991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your deduction skills and your horror movies knowledge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791460/extras/204eff9ddb6909b3494eb7dc1f0f9a1e.avif?t=1639777991\" width=600 height=186 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >See plot summary of the movies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791460/extras/ac8d0e10983aa7e6e0417b5a647ffa4f.avif?t=1639777991\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some filmemojis are hard to guess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791460/extras/0b4f104b58dafc9df07f90b66430cc73.avif?t=1639777991\" width=600 height=186 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100 handcrafted horror movies filmemojis to guess.<br></li><li> Original soundtrack.<br></li><li> Halloween theme.<br></li><li> Type the answer with keyboard or click in buttons with mouse.<br></li><li> Plot summary of the movies.<br></li><li> It's pretty hard to guess alone all filmemojis.<br></li><li> Has hidden achievments...</li></ul>",
